{"tid":2087582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IPAC對國安法實施回應","createTime":"2020-06-30T17:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T00:50:40.000Z","uid":360675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"401c78b466143809d0361f73ebe57eca89a83d18","tid":2087582,"uid":360675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1TNh4Wd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1TNh4Wd.jpg&h=ba9bffd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨便google translate<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n我們是中國議會聯盟聯盟的成員，我們譴責中國人大在香港實施所謂的《國家安全法》。 這項新法律是對這座城市的基本自由，法治和自治的全面攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n 《中英聯合聲明》（根據國際法具有約束力的條約），《香港基本法》和《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》保證了香港的高度自治和生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n 北京實施這項立法，明顯違反了其對香港公民的條約義務，將嚴重損害700萬香港公民的權利，並對國際社會構成嚴峻挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n 這些動作不能無解。 任何國家都不能不受懲罰地違反國際準則和協議。<br />\n<br />\n 議會，政府，七國集團，國際機構以及其他無數人反對單方面強加《國家安全法》。 中華人民共和國領導人沒有聽從他們的警告。 現在應該明確後果了。<br />\n<br />\n 因此，我們呼籲各國政府：<br />\n<br />\n 在同盟國和合作夥伴的協調下，審查並重新調整與中華人民共和國的關係，提出立法，以加快已經進行的努力，以在國家和國際層面上審核和減少對中國的戰略依賴。<br />\n<br />\n 通過由民主國家聯盟組織的國際&ldquo;救生艇&rdquo;計劃，為處於遭受迫害危險中的香港公民提供保護。<br />\n<br />\n 要求聯合國秘書長指定聯合國特使對香港進行監測和報告。<br />\n<br />\n 在踐踏香港公民的權利和違反國際義務的同時，國際社會不能袖手旁觀。 為了這個偉大城市的人民，為了維護全球和平，民主價值觀和法治，世界必須團結起來捍衛香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1277987482596970498?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1277987482596970498%3Fs%3D21&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=80bd1c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1277987482596970498%3Fs%3D21&h=2eb21147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1277987482596970498?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"5c8899b0db9403ddf1b67c6e501f214c55d0f628","tid":2087582,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"只有眼前路，沒有身後身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路"},{"pid":"5a97ca762aae44458fc589d8e747bcf0aed939d3","tid":2087582,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"叫埋IPAC 取消引渡協議....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a042fcfd2f1129eb69ccd3946d7b7d10d124ef9","tid":2087582,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得, 推番行動POST優先"},{"pid":"c91c966e0af556862dd486328025aa674994cc08","tid":2087582,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"咩組織黎？"},{"pid":"92bd6b759880d19f91ae1444b31c4abb2e3ac4a7","tid":2087582,"uid":360675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c91c966e0af556862dd486328025aa674994cc08","tid":2087582,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"咩組織黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200605/YBJIL5OZYUV2B75RAAM6VDPLLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FYBJIL5OZYUV2B75RAAM6VDPLLY%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=2dd712b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FYBJIL5OZYUV2B75RAAM6VDPLLY%2F&h=2b3047ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200605/YBJIL5OZYUV2B75RAAM6VDPLLY/</a>"}]}